{"tid":770921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實互相鍾意既話 係咪一定要一齊呢？","createTime":"2018-08-07T13:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T13:33:20.000Z","uid":16425,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b5aebfe5ef2464049c631756f6ffc80aa629d7","tid":770921,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"假設兩個人唔係情侶 但都可以好恩愛咁好似情侶咁一齊相處 仲需唔需要一個情侶既名份呢？"},{"pid":"0b1b6a76d1e95cabf38d2e029d6595caafe8686a","tid":770921,"uid":28741,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"返屋企打飛機啦你"},{"pid":"338870d73612fed823a85cecfc7ebf2255105a8f","tid":770921,"uid":143344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"Gay就唔洗"},{"pid":"c2cc03dac39eae4a8131e529bd9f7c54265bdf0f","tid":770921,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"會用兄弟代替情侶"},{"pid":"fee248c2f9341aafe4af5b8a82a01952c679fd4b","tid":770921,"uid":152612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"如果一齊到既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7d39277b7e21aa55a3027aa993797e84290c7b","tid":770921,"uid":140798,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"咁佢可以同個個都咁做"},{"pid":"769a368a6c55a701b13008dcde6822cded4951da","tid":770921,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"我諗得比較簡單 覺得既然互相鍾意就一齊得啦<br />\n但對方唔係咁諗 諗既野比較多 比較長遠<br />\n覺得未放到我第一 咁樣驚大家辛苦<br />\n同埋太多未知之數 未ready好同我一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd81c20e505e4df860ffb1bfad055678bc8327f0","tid":770921,"uid":21355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"以結婚為前提一齊嘅話一定係諗得比較多先決定一唔一齊"},{"pid":"32e55db340b103e2ebf78729d9ff99d0baa554ec","tid":770921,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"諗諗下 其實而家差個名份姐 但同佢相處都好開心呀<br />\n係既 佢唔係放我係第一 但起碼我都算有少少少少位置呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba35ea64949fb60183892339cddd0f6dd2f3ae6d","tid":770921,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7d39277b7e21aa55a3027aa993797e84290c7b","tid":770921,"uid":140798,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"咁佢可以同個個都咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:23:12.000Z","msg":"其實都係 因為你唔係佢邊個"},{"pid":"99ca3c810e65a0980e4bec7b4d30bbb572797e1e","tid":770921,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀"},{"pid":"35f2c690613a7f71caf9b0397ec716784f35578b","tid":770921,"uid":29320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"你覺得你地真係鐘意你？定係做兵咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪試下表白囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba139ff209aa9c37ec126da3a779e7000729c8b7","tid":770921,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99ca3c810e65a0980e4bec7b4d30bbb572797e1e","tid":770921,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:28:02.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就殺了她。大不了就被殺，你連投胎都不敢還好意思說愛她。投胎長大之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81798189c018dd372195c1f599c419e4a3c0c1b","tid":770921,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35f2c690613a7f71caf9b0397ec716784f35578b","tid":